main event: Mrs. [REDACTED] observed a reddish-orange object in the sky while traveling in an automobile on 26 July 1960.
interesting points: The object was observed for approximately 15 minutes and appeared to be pulsating and stationary,The sighting took place while traveling at speeds of 70-80 mph,The object rapidly faded out and disappeared through a haze layer, Mrs. [REDACTED]'s 7-year-old daughter first drew attention to the object,The incident was not corroborated by service station attendants in the area.
